    "body": "I suspect we may want to disable opportunity fire by default on aircraft. It feels really weird in TD (which doesn't have limited ammo, so doesn't default to hold fire) because apaches will fire on anything immediately in front of it when flying overhead, but not anything even slightly off to the side."
