    "updated_at": "2019-04-02T14:09:18Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Agree with pchote to disable opportunity fire by default on aircraft, it does not feel right in RA when ammunition is a rare commodity and units fire rather unpredictable. I find it also harder to micro MiGs with opportunity fire than with direct targeting. Personally I find the concept good for turreted units (decoupled moving / targeting) but don't really like it for units that can only attack frontal."
