    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Looking at the comments in that PR and the previous PR it doesn't strike me as strong negative feedback, just mild concerns about the reduced ability to concentrate fire on a single target. That concern is not warranted here, because this changes nothing about the attack behaviour in the default stance. It only adds new behaviour in the more aggresive stances that is in line with how stances work for other units (whereas up till now the more aggresive stances didn't function at all). This is a win-win.\r\n\r\n"
